---

<section
    class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative py-32 bg-[#022c22] text-[#ccfbf1] overflow-hidden"
>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-10">
        <svg class="w-full h-full">
            <pattern
                id="piPattern"
                x="0"
                y="0"
                width="60"
                height="60"
                patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
            >
                <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="2" fill="#5eead4"></circle>
                <path d="M 0 30 L 60 30 M 30 0 L 30 60" stroke="#2dd4bf" stroke-width="0.5"></path>
            </pattern>
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#115e59" filter="url(#piPattern)"></rect>
        </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-8">
                <span
                    class="text-[#5eead4] font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase border-b border-[#2dd4bf] pb-2"
                    >El Límite Inalcanzable</span
                >
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif italic text-[#f0fdfa]">
                    La Paradoja de Pi
                </h2>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed font-serif text-[#ccfbf1]/90">
                    ¿Cuántas veces cabe el diámetro en su circunferencia? Tres veces, y un poco más.
                    Ese "poco más" es un abismo infinito.
                </p>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6">
                    <div
                        class="bg-[#134e4a]/60 p-4 rounded-sm border border-[#2dd4bf]/30 backdrop-blur-sm transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300"
                    >
                        <h3 class="text-[#f0fdfa] font-bold mb-1 text-lg">3.14159...</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-[#99f6e4] leading-relaxed">
                            No es solo infinito, es irracional. Ninguna fracción 22/7 puede
                            contenerlo. Es una verdad que no se puede escribir.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="bg-[#134e4a]/60 p-4 rounded-sm border border-[#2dd4bf]/30 backdrop-blur-sm transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300"
                    >
                        <h3 class="text-[#f0fdfa] font-bold mb-1 text-lg">Exhaustión</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-[#99f6e4] leading-relaxed">
                            Arquímedes atrapó al círculo entre polígonos. 96 lados le dieron 3.14.
                            Pero el círculo siempre escapa entre los vértices.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="bg-[#134e4a]/60 p-4 rounded-sm border border-[#2dd4bf]/30 backdrop-blur-sm transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300 sm:col-span-2"
                    >
                        <h3 class="text-[#f0fdfa] font-bold mb-1 text-lg">Trascendente</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-[#99f6e4] leading-relaxed">
                            Pi no es la raíz de ninguna ecuación algebraica simple. Es un número que
                            existe fuera de las reglas básicas del álgebra, un recordatorio de que
                            el universo es más complejo que nuestras fórmulas.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex justify-center relative h-[400px]">
                <div class="relative w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" class="w-full h-full overflow-visible">
                        <circle
                            cx="200"
                            cy="200"
                            r="150"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="#5eead4"
                            stroke-width="1"
                            opacity="0.2"></circle>

                        <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="3" fill="#f0fdfa"></circle>

                        <g transform="translate(200, 200)">
                            <polygon
                                points="0,-150 150,0 0,150 -150,0"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="#f0fdfa"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                class="polygon-anim opacity-0"
                                style="animation-delay: 0s;"></polygon>

                            <polygon
                                points="150,0 75,129.9 -75,129.9 -150,0 -75,-129.9 75,-129.9"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="#f0fdfa"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                class="polygon-anim opacity-0"
                                style="animation-delay: 2s;"></polygon>

                            <polygon
                                points="150,0 129.9,75 75,129.9 0,150 -75,129.9 -129.9,75 -150,0 -129.9,-75 -75,-129.9 0,-150 75,-129.9 129.9,-75"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="#f0fdfa"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                class="polygon-anim opacity-0"
                                style="animation-delay: 4s;"></polygon>

                            <circle
                                r="150"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="#2dd4bf"
                                stroke-width="3"
                                class="polygon-anim opacity-0"
                                style="animation-delay: 6s;"></circle>
                        </g>

                        <text
                            x="200"
                            y="380"
                            text-anchor="middle"
                            class="text-sm font-mono fill-[#5eead4] tracking-widest uppercase"
                        >
                            <tspan class="text-anim" style="animation-delay: 0s;">n = 4</tspan>
                            <tspan class="text-anim" style="animation-delay: 2s;">n = 6</tspan>
                            <tspan class="text-anim" style="animation-delay: 4s;">n = 12</tspan>
                            <tspan class="text-anim" style="animation-delay: 6s;">n = ∞</tspan>
                        </text>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .polygon-anim,
    .text-anim {
        animation-name: sequenceFade;
        animation-duration: 8s;
        animation-iteration-count: infinite;
        opacity: 0;
    }

    @keyframes sequenceFade {
        0%,
        20% {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        25%,
        100% {
            opacity: 0;
        }
    }

    .polygon-anim:nth-child(1),
    .text-anim:nth-child(1) {
        animation-delay: 0s;
    }
    .polygon-anim:nth-child(2),
    .text-anim:nth-child(2) {
        animation-delay: 2s;
    }
    .polygon-anim:nth-child(3),
    .text-anim:nth-child(3) {
        animation-delay: 4s;
    }
    .polygon-anim:nth-child(4),
    .text-anim:nth-child(4) {
        animation-delay: 6s;
    }
</style>
